Module com.example.froggeroop
Package com.example.froggeroop.util

Class WindowList<T>

java.lang.Object
com.example.froggeroop.util.WindowList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of object making up the list
public class WindowList<T> extends Object
Special data structure that manages a list of items and a sublist of this list. The sublist, of a fixed length, can move forward or backward over the list
